1
00:01:27,430 --> 00:01:31,940
[The Dark Romance]

2
00:01:32,250 --> 00:01:34,950
[Episode 7]

3
00:02:00,890 --> 00:02:02,490
-Miss Wang, hurry up.
-Okay.

4
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,320
Which one of you is the killer's parent?

5
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:27,670
Attorney Zhou and I represent Yuan Ye.

6
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,150
And these two are...

7
00:02:28,150 --> 00:02:30,010
These two are Yuan Ye's teachers.

8
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:32,240
Sit down. Okay?

9
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,570
Let's sit down and talk.

10
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:36,120
The killer's parents
don't even dare show up.

11
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,190
What's there to talk about?

12
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:37,840
Mr. Xu,

13
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,000
it's not that Yuan Ye's parents
didn't want to come,

14
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,400
but they truly couldn't.

15
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:44,120
Five years ago,
her mother killed her father.

16
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,780
She's currently serving time

17
00:02:45,870 --> 00:02:47,270
for negligent homicide.

18
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:48,970
I didn't know that.

19
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:52,829
Look at the kind of people you mess with.

20
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,360
She lied to me.

21
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,400
Stupid.

22
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:01,520
I am the victim's representative lawyer.

23
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:04,000
After taking all the actual circumstances
into consideration,

24
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,310
Mr. Xu, in a spirit of generosity,

25
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,590
is willing to propose a settlement
covering medical expenses,

26
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:10,240
hospitalization meal subsidies,

27
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,590
nursing care, nutrition,

28
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:13,820
transportation,

29
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,310
and compensation for emotional distress,

30
00:03:15,310 --> 00:03:16,710
totaling 1 million yuan.

31
00:03:18,590 --> 00:03:19,310
Settlement

32
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:20,800
was proposed by you.

33
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,760
If the conditions cannot be met,

34
00:03:23,030 --> 00:03:24,290
we'll see you in court.

35
00:03:24,630 --> 00:03:25,400
Mr. Xu,

36
00:03:26,570 --> 00:03:28,910
the two of them did have a relationship,

37
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,360
and at the time of the incident

38
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,630
neither side was calm.

39
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,520
Xu Feng,

40
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:36,520
you wouldn't want your former girlfriend

41
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,720
to spend her youth in prison, would you?

42
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:42,050
Given my client's special
family circumstances,

43
00:03:42,050 --> 00:03:43,650
1 million is indeed too much.

44
00:03:43,750 --> 00:03:45,550
Then what's there to talk about?

45
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,750
Excuse me.

46
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:51,760
Can I say a few words?

47
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:55,380
I didn't introduce myself
properly earlier.

48
00:03:55,380 --> 00:03:57,960
I'm a psychiatrist
at Renxin Municipal Hospital.

49
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,090
My name is Luo Liang.

50
00:03:59,690 --> 00:04:02,190
Attorney Zhou and Xiang invited me
to attend the hearing,

51
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:04,440
mainly hoping to take this opportunity

52
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,690
for me to explain Yuan Ye's situation.

53
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,600
What Xu Feng just said

54
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:09,630
was the truth.

55
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,680
When Yuan Ye was dating him,

56
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,260
she did lie about her family background.

57
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:16,120
Mr. Xu,

58
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:19,000
young people aren't as
mature and steady as you,

59
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,870
nor have they been through
life's ups and downs.

60
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:22,630
They're simple and easily trusting—

61
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:24,030
that's understandable.

62
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,550
It also shows that Xu Feng is,

63
00:04:25,550 --> 00:04:27,310
at heart, kind and sincere,

64
00:04:27,740 --> 00:04:29,270
a testament to your fine upbringing

65
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:30,470
and his good fortune.

66
00:04:31,570 --> 00:04:32,490
But Yuan Ye

67
00:04:34,210 --> 00:04:36,070
hasn't been nearly as fortunate.

68
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,800
Ever since she was old enough to remember,

69
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,240
she had been dragged around by her mother,

70
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,680
chasing down her father—

71
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:41,930
trying to catch him cheating,

72
00:04:41,930 --> 00:04:43,330
going after mistresses.

73
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,370
You seduced my husband!

74
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:56,280
I'll kill you!
How dare you seduce my husband?

75
00:04:59,270 --> 00:05:00,190
You home-wrecker!

76
00:05:00,190 --> 00:05:00,800
Get out!

77
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:01,620
Get out!

78
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:03,480
Get out!

79
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:07,530
You can't keep your own husband in check!

80
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,280
Are you done?

81
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:12,160
You bring the child every time!

82
00:05:15,310 --> 00:05:17,510
Endless arguments between her parents

83
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:21,750
and extremely irrational violence

84
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:22,560
and beatings

85
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,650
were her main childhood memories.

86
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:31,380
Excuse me,

87
00:05:32,620 --> 00:05:33,430
is there

88
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:35,040
a girl named Yuan Ye living around here?

89
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,470
Yes, on the third floor.

90
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:37,870
Until 5 years ago,

91
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:39,800
Yuan Ye, having just graduated from
a vocational high school,

92
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,540
witnessed her mother,

93
00:05:41,670 --> 00:05:44,750
unable to tolerate her
repeatedly cheating father anymore,

94
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:45,830
grab an axe

95
00:05:46,340 --> 00:05:47,220
in a fit of rage

96
00:05:48,090 --> 00:05:49,420
and hack at her husband,

97
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,909
thus

98
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,330
causing an irreversible tragedy.

99
00:06:01,190 --> 00:06:02,450
This unfortunate girl

100
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,160
has never experienced

101
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:06,240
a healthy relationship.

102
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,560
She yearned for love,

103
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:10,790
but doesn't know how to love.

104
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,280
What she needs

105
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:14,080
is not just punishment,

106
00:06:14,610 --> 00:06:16,990
but perhaps more guidance and help.

107
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:20,150
Just as Mr. Xu questioned
at the beginning,

108
00:06:20,390 --> 00:06:22,120
none of us are Yuan Ye's family.

109
00:06:22,220 --> 00:06:23,670
But we came here today,

110
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,920
primarily hoping to act on her behalf

111
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,480
to seek your forgiveness.

112
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:28,680
After all,

113
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:31,330
her childhood and birth
were not her choice.

114
00:06:31,630 --> 00:06:32,560
But you

115
00:06:33,270 --> 00:06:35,770
can give a child
who has temporarily gone astray

116
00:06:35,770 --> 00:06:37,680
a chance to start over.

117
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,830
Please.

118
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:43,159
Mr. Xu.

119
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,600
You mean

120
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:49,180
she is justified because she is weak,

121
00:06:49,270 --> 00:06:49,950
so our

122
00:06:49,950 --> 00:06:50,750
carefully raised,

123
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:51,870
healthy kids

124
00:06:52,390 --> 00:06:53,870
deserve to be hurt by her?

125
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:56,970
If being excusable means being forgivable,

126
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:58,630
then what is the law for?

127
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:01,630
Xu Feng,

128
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,540
what do you say?

129
00:07:14,610 --> 00:07:15,980
Teaching her a lesson

130
00:07:17,410 --> 00:07:18,870
is the best choice for her.

131
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:22,510
Xu Feng,

132
00:07:23,030 --> 00:07:24,390
you repeatedly

133
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,610
dated several girls at the same time.

134
00:07:26,610 --> 00:07:29,040
You deliberately
provoked Yuan Ye's emotions.

135
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:31,170
But she was completely sincere to you.

136
00:07:31,810 --> 00:07:33,560
Even now, she is still

137
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:35,310
suffering and blaming herself
for hurting you,

138
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:36,770
and wishing she were dead.

139
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,780
Don't you have any compassion at all?

140
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:44,000
Is it illegal to date

141
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:45,800
multiple girlfriends at once?

142
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,600
They were only with him

143
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:50,190
because he had my money in his pocket.

144
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,950
Now that they've broken up,

145
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:53,810
she goes crazy and stabs someone;

146
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:55,070
does a person like her

147
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,330
deserve any sympathy?

148
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:03,720
Xu Feng,

149
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,450
can I have a word with you alone?

150
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:33,809
Sorry.

151
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:36,030
I couldn't be of any help.

152
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:37,470
You did your best.

153
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,950
It was actually expected.

154
00:08:40,950 --> 00:08:43,280
The victim's family isn't short on money,

155
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:45,510
and judging from their attitude,

156
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:47,840
there's hardly any room for negotiation.

157
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:57,550
Here's the thing.

158
00:08:58,230 --> 00:08:59,200
Mr. Xu and his son

159
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:01,680
have taken the other family's
circumstances into consideration.

160
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:03,680
They've agreed to reduce the compensation

161
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:06,000
and have signed a letter of understanding.

162
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,560
As for the specific settlement terms,

163
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:09,960
I'll be handling the negotiations in full.

164
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,830
What exactly did you say to Xu Feng?

165
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:16,200
A few words made him change his mind.

166
00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:19,450
I didn't actually say much to him.

167
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:21,850
Have you ever heard

168
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,490
of intergenerational transmission?

169
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,530
What do you mean?

170
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,510
It means the parents' behaviors and ideas

171
00:09:27,510 --> 00:09:29,840
are subtly passed down to their children.

172
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,200
Yuan Ye's mother killed her father.

173
00:09:32,250 --> 00:09:33,500
If Yuan Ye finds out

174
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:35,270
that Xu Feng doesn't forgive her

175
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:37,270
and even agrees to let her go to jail,

176
00:09:37,370 --> 00:09:38,770
it could cause a huge blow

177
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,360
to Yuan Ye's mind.

178
00:09:41,010 --> 00:09:42,360
Maybe after she gets out of prison,

179
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:44,220
she won't let Xu Feng off the hook.

180
00:09:44,770 --> 00:09:45,630
I just explained

181
00:09:45,630 --> 00:09:47,040
this concept to Xu Feng.

182
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,910
I knew it.

183
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:54,810
People like you who have moral obsessions

184
00:09:54,810 --> 00:09:56,720
would never accept me saying that.

185
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,440
No, no.

186
00:09:58,390 --> 00:10:00,250
Actually, I could guess a little.

187
00:10:00,270 --> 00:10:02,070
Because after you talked to him,

188
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:04,740
I saw fear in his eyes.

189
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,250
He should be afraid.

190
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:08,790
Making him afraid

191
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:12,000
finally got us a decent result.

192
00:10:12,660 --> 00:10:14,120
Shouldn't we celebrate

193
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,250
and have a nice meal?

194
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,950
I really should treat you to a nice meal

195
00:10:17,950 --> 00:10:19,010
to appreciate you.

196
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:20,510
I didn't even know

197
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:23,800
you went to investigate
Yuan Ye's family situation.

198
00:10:24,140 --> 00:10:25,340
Do you remember this?

199
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:27,760
What is it?

200
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:31,670
The first time we went to Xu Feng's school

201
00:10:31,670 --> 00:10:32,630
and met Yuan Ye,

202
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:33,550
didn't you get really angry

203
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:35,410
and slam a lighter onto the table?

204
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,440
I've been to this nightclub.

205
00:10:39,750 --> 00:10:41,610
It turns out Yuan Ye worked there.

206
00:10:42,010 --> 00:10:43,870
Then I found out about her family,

207
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:47,010
and learned they had
this kind of story behind them.

208
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:48,760
Really, thank you

209
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,240
for doing so much for her.

210
00:10:51,710 --> 00:10:52,460
But...

211
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,540
After all that buildup of gratitude,

212
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,510
aren't you just leading up to saying

213
00:10:59,510 --> 00:11:02,190
you don't have time
to have dinner with me?

214
00:11:03,390 --> 00:11:03,960
No, no.

215
00:11:04,070 --> 00:11:05,050
Actually, it's okay.

216
00:11:05,050 --> 00:11:07,740
Every time I ask you out for a meal,
I'm just pushing my luck.

217
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:09,790
I'm already very used to
being rejected by you.

218
00:11:09,790 --> 00:11:11,120
That's not what I meant.

219
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,150
By the way,

220
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:20,360
I washed your clothes.

221
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,190
Thank you.

222
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:21,970
That's good.

223
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,250
I'll pick the place.

224
00:11:23,370 --> 00:11:25,400
I'll take this time to go home,

225
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:27,350
take a shower, and change clothes.

226
00:11:28,230 --> 00:11:29,760
Does it have to be so formal?

227
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:32,410
Of course. The sense of ceremony
is important.

228
00:11:32,410 --> 00:11:34,240
We can't just meet every time

229
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:36,030
dressed like we're going to work.

230
00:11:36,030 --> 00:11:38,440
You can always put on a nice outfit

231
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:40,000
and have a relaxing meal.

232
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:44,470
Then I have to go home and change.

233
00:11:44,660 --> 00:11:46,120
Dinner will be even later.

234
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,040
It's okay.

235
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:49,820
To see a different side of you,

236
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,610
it's worth the wait.

237
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,270
[Police]

238
00:12:00,030 --> 00:12:05,750
[The chips are delicious.
The chips are delicious.]

239
00:12:11,470 --> 00:12:13,500
[China Police]

240
00:12:13,570 --> 00:12:17,220
[The chips are delicious.
The chips are delicious.]

241
00:12:20,630 --> 00:12:22,130
No wonder.

242
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:24,120
Wait, you...

243
00:12:26,610 --> 00:12:27,650
Aren't you the...

244
00:12:28,630 --> 00:12:29,760
You're our comrade.

245
00:12:30,270 --> 00:12:30,960
What's up?

246
00:12:31,780 --> 00:12:32,700
[China Police]

247
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:33,590
[Name: Pongsri Leekpa]

248
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,970
How do you have this?

249
00:12:43,150 --> 00:12:44,750
It's exactly the same. Look.

250
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:46,880
Come with me.

251
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,420
Where are we going?

252
00:12:57,210 --> 00:13:02,560
[China Police]

253
00:13:17,010 --> 00:13:18,870
Does the task force provide food?

254
00:13:19,390 --> 00:13:19,790
Yes.

255
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:23,840
Can I use my institute meal card

256
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:25,200
in the task force?

257
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:25,840
No.

258
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:30,720
It's fine.

259
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:36,910
Clear this area.

260
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,290
Clear this area.

261
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:44,720
Who is it?

262
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,420
What are you doing?

263
00:13:49,700 --> 00:13:51,570
We just finished eating.

264
00:13:51,710 --> 00:13:52,720
Hold it up!

265
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,440
This...

266
00:13:54,910 --> 00:13:56,570
You're playing a game, right?

267
00:13:57,550 --> 00:13:59,050
I'm not going to scold you.

268
00:13:59,070 --> 00:14:00,330
Why are you so nervous?

269
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:01,510
It's a new game.

270
00:14:01,900 --> 00:14:03,750
Dad and I have been waiting for days.

271
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:05,070
We make a great team.

272
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:06,450
Listen to Dad.

273
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:08,210
I'm home. I'll hang up now.

274
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:25,840
Dr. Luo,

275
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:26,600
I'm home.

276
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:29,910
Don't move.

277
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:31,360
Who are you? What are you doing?

278
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:32,960
Is there anyone else in the house?

279
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:33,440
Yes!

280
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:35,820
Where are they?

281
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,080
Come out!

282
00:14:37,670 --> 00:14:39,030
People in the room, come out!

283
00:14:39,030 --> 00:14:39,790
Liu Ping?

284
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:43,770
What do you want?

285
00:14:43,870 --> 00:14:45,200
I'm calling the police!

286
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,480
You dare call the police?

287
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,880
You dare call the police?

288
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:49,430
You dare call the police?

289
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,910
Tell me, where is she?

290
00:14:51,510 --> 00:14:53,040
Where did you hide Yu Kexin?

291
00:14:53,550 --> 00:14:53,950
She...

292
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:56,200
She went back to Australia
to find her mom.

293
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:58,080
Bullshit! What Australia?

294
00:14:58,080 --> 00:14:59,080
What Mom?

295
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:00,950
You are all lying to me!

296
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:02,470
Why would I lie to you?

297
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:03,800
What did I lie about?

298
00:15:04,150 --> 00:15:06,210
I personally took her to the airport.

299
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:08,810
I saw her walk in with my own eyes.

300
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:10,960
Please calm down.

301
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:12,310
Don't be impulsive.

302
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,580
Put the knife down, okay?

303
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,960
She's still pregnant with your child.

304
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,840
She wouldn't lie to you.

305
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:22,840
Bullshit! What child?

306
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:24,240
It's all fake!

307
00:15:25,390 --> 00:15:27,120
I don't even know

308
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,450
if I've ever had a child.

309
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:34,680
What do you mean?

310
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,320
I don't understand.

311
00:15:42,910 --> 00:15:45,320
After we finalized the divorce,
I moved out.

312
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,000
A few days ago,

313
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:48,060
property management called and said

314
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,720
the bathroom was leaking

315
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:52,320
and flooded the apartment downstairs.

316
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:54,510
So I tried to get it fixed.

317
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,590
But when I called her,

318
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:59,080
the number was out of service.

319
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:02,390
I checked and she canceled the number.

320
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:04,390
So I had to rush home.

321
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:07,120
I found out she had moved out
a long time ago.

322
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:09,440
She just left a key

323
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:12,100
with the property management
to sell the house.

324
00:16:12,390 --> 00:16:13,360
That's normal.

325
00:16:14,270 --> 00:16:17,330
She probably wanted to
make a clean break with the past.

326
00:16:17,510 --> 00:16:19,150
I thought so too at first,

327
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:21,120
but then I found this.

328
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:25,430
What is this?

329
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:28,080
It's a benzodiazepine-based,

330
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:30,080
highly potent sedative-hypnotic.

331
00:16:30,270 --> 00:16:32,960
It's a strictly controlled
psychotropic drug.

332
00:16:33,150 --> 00:16:35,630
It is commonly known as
obedience powder or date rape pills.

333
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:37,670
It's even more potent
when mixed with alcohol.

334
00:16:37,670 --> 00:16:38,550
Looking at this packaging,

335
00:16:38,550 --> 00:16:40,670
it might have been illegally imported
from abroad.

336
00:16:40,670 --> 00:16:41,480
Xinxin,

337
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:44,480
get me a glass of water.

338
00:16:49,390 --> 00:16:50,320
Xinxin!

339
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,160
Xinxin!

340
00:17:05,589 --> 00:17:06,310
Xinxin!

341
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,109
Xinxin!

342
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:13,000
Xinxin!

343
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,349
You mean

344
00:17:20,349 --> 00:17:22,200
Yu Kexin gave you this drug

345
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:25,329
and then faked a domestic violence scene?

346
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:26,109
Then,

347
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:28,750
what about the injuries on her body?

348
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:31,980
She couldn't have beaten herself up?

349
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:34,620
Anyway, it definitely wasn't me.

350
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,290
The doctor also said

351
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:38,660
that this medicine
knocks you out completely.

352
00:17:38,660 --> 00:17:40,310
I had no ability to move at all.

353
00:17:40,310 --> 00:17:42,710
How could I have the strength
to hit anyone?

354
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,160
How could someone

355
00:17:45,110 --> 00:17:46,880
be so cruel to themselves?

356
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,880
She's also pregnant.

357
00:17:53,110 --> 00:17:55,070
The domestic abuse was fake—

358
00:17:56,030 --> 00:17:57,830
how could the pregnancy be real?

359
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:00,270
Later, I checked

360
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,260
every OB-GYN hospital

361
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:04,510
in Lihai City.

362
00:18:04,510 --> 00:18:05,640
There's no record of

363
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:08,310
her ever visiting

364
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:10,380
or registering at any of them.

365
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:15,200
The most important thing for you now

366
00:18:15,270 --> 00:18:16,870
is to take care of your health

367
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,310
and stay emotionally stable.

368
00:18:18,310 --> 00:18:21,110
After all, you're responsible for
two people now.

369
00:18:24,750 --> 00:18:26,400
I can raise you on my own,

370
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:27,990
can't I?

371
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:30,350
This is too absurd.

372
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:32,100
She came to me

373
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:33,790
to borrow money

374
00:18:33,790 --> 00:18:35,110
so she could hide out for a few days.

375
00:18:35,110 --> 00:18:35,820
She said

376
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,720
all her money was with you.

377
00:18:38,590 --> 00:18:39,920
I've seen her Weibo.

378
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:41,570
She's quite wealthy

379
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,330
and even has a house.

380
00:18:44,850 --> 00:18:48,070
[Clairet Xin, Stay Happy]

381
00:18:48,730 --> 00:18:50,530
She deleted all her Weibo posts.

382
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:57,550
Later, I went to that so-called home

383
00:18:57,550 --> 00:18:58,410
to look for her.

384
00:18:59,000 --> 00:19:00,860
She said her mom bought it for her,

385
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:03,030
but actually,

386
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:05,200
that house was rented

387
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:07,780
and only for a little over two months.

388
00:19:08,790 --> 00:19:09,990
After we got married,

389
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:12,820
it was always me giving her money.

390
00:19:13,510 --> 00:19:15,710
She didn't leave a single penny with me.

391
00:19:17,310 --> 00:19:18,000
The tattoo.

392
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:20,930
I found you because of the tattoo.

393
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:24,110
She said you got that tattoo

394
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:26,270
for her.

395
00:19:27,590 --> 00:19:29,640
Did you know she took out a nude loan?

396
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,480
What nude loan?

397
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,070
She made me

398
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:37,000
get this tattoo when we got married—

399
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:39,390
kept pushing me until I gave in,

400
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:41,440
said it was to commemorate our love.

401
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:42,160
This...

402
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:45,130
Liu Ping, aren't you disgusted?

403
00:19:45,130 --> 00:19:46,900
I never thought you were
this kind of person.

404
00:19:46,900 --> 00:19:47,830
No, no.

405
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:49,070
Xinxin.

406
00:19:49,070 --> 00:19:49,800
Listen to me.

407
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:50,350
Xinxin.

408
00:19:50,350 --> 00:19:51,030
Don't touch me!

409
00:19:51,030 --> 00:19:52,090
Xinxin, I'm not...

410
00:19:52,550 --> 00:19:54,590
It's really not what you think.

411
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:55,750
I called a few

412
00:19:55,750 --> 00:19:57,160
colleagues

413
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:59,460
who were working overtime,
both men and women.

414
00:19:59,460 --> 00:20:02,190
Are female colleagues
necessarily good people?

415
00:20:02,510 --> 00:20:04,550
If there's really nothing between you two,

416
00:20:04,550 --> 00:20:06,440
why is her hair on you?

417
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:08,480
I... I don't know either.

418
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:09,340
You don't know?

419
00:20:10,070 --> 00:20:10,960
Xinxin.

420
00:20:11,030 --> 00:20:13,400
Calm down.

421
00:20:13,510 --> 00:20:13,880
I...

422
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:15,120
Phone.

423
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:16,230
Phone.

424
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:17,240
Phone.

425
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:18,000
Here.

426
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:21,440
I'll call your colleagues right now.

427
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:22,510
I'll call them one by one

428
00:20:22,510 --> 00:20:23,590
and ask them clearly

429
00:20:23,590 --> 00:20:24,680
what exactly is going on!

430
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:25,480
Xinxin, I beg you.

431
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,070
Calm down.

432
00:20:26,070 --> 00:20:27,720
Really. We're married.

433
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:29,440
I couldn't possibly be involved with
another woman.

434
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:29,880
Is that so?

435
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:30,550
Then swear it.

436
00:20:30,550 --> 00:20:31,640
I swear.

437
00:20:31,830 --> 00:20:34,110
I, Liu Ping,

438
00:20:34,110 --> 00:20:35,750
I swear, well...

439
00:20:35,750 --> 00:20:37,210
You can't even swear properly!

440
00:20:37,210 --> 00:20:39,200
Do you think just talking is enough?

441
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:40,480
Why should I believe you?

442
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:41,240
I...

443
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:44,580
I'm asking you
how you're going to prove it to me.

444
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:46,070
Xinxin.

445
00:20:46,070 --> 00:20:47,400
Xinxin, calm down.

446
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:49,790
Xinxin, don't be angry anymore.

447
00:20:52,070 --> 00:20:53,110
I'll prove it

448
00:20:53,110 --> 00:20:54,370
however you want me to.

449
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,400
Don't be angry anymore.

450
00:20:56,400 --> 00:20:57,330
I'm begging you.

451
00:20:58,640 --> 00:20:59,770
Then go get a tattoo.

452
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:01,280
A tattoo?

453
00:21:04,820 --> 00:21:07,080
Get the exact same design tattooed on you

454
00:21:07,240 --> 00:21:08,300
to prove you love me

455
00:21:08,460 --> 00:21:10,430
and that you belong only to me.

456
00:21:10,590 --> 00:21:11,480
If any woman

457
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:12,830
sees this design on you,

458
00:21:12,830 --> 00:21:14,440
I curse the two of you adulterers

459
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:15,770
to die a horrible death.

460
00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:19,940
Xinxin.

461
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:23,020
You don't agree?

462
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:25,590
No.

463
00:21:28,110 --> 00:21:29,440
I want you to get a tattoo

464
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:32,200
just to prove you love me

465
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:34,860
and that you belong only to me.

466
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:38,510
Because I love Leilei.

467
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:40,240
Since I love her,

468
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:41,310
I must love all of her,

469
00:21:41,310 --> 00:21:43,270
including her flaws.

470
00:21:43,590 --> 00:21:44,720
I was forced by the creditors

471
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:47,470
to get a tattoo as they demanded.

472
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:48,930
The tattoo on Leilei

473
00:21:49,830 --> 00:21:51,350
was probably also done

474
00:21:51,350 --> 00:21:52,810
as these people demanded.

475
00:21:57,110 --> 00:21:58,710
Hello. Is Officer Li there?

476
00:21:58,920 --> 00:21:59,810
Who is this?

477
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:01,000
My name is Yan Ling.

478
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:02,350
I'm a friend of a client

479
00:22:02,350 --> 00:22:03,400
from one of his previous cases.

480
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:05,400
I have some information to tell him.

481
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:07,680
He's left for the provincial department.

482
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:08,610
He left?

483
00:22:08,790 --> 00:22:09,960
The task force is confidential.

484
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:11,090
He can't be reached.

485
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:11,960
You can't get away.

486
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:12,790
Let me tell you,

487
00:22:12,790 --> 00:22:14,350
I'm not done with you today.

488
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:15,510
-You can't get away.
-What are you doing?

489
00:22:15,510 --> 00:22:16,270
Someone!

490
00:22:16,290 --> 00:22:20,650
[Police]

491
00:22:20,970 --> 00:22:23,820
[110 Emergency Call Center – Service Hall]

492
00:22:31,110 --> 00:22:33,740
Hello. The number you dialed
is out of service.

493
00:22:33,820 --> 00:22:35,420
Please check and dial again.

494
00:22:42,510 --> 00:22:45,210
Hello. The number you dialed
is out of service.

495
00:22:45,240 --> 00:22:46,840
Please check and dial again.

496
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:55,510
I was forced by the creditors

497
00:22:55,510 --> 00:22:56,370
to follow their

498
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:58,280
demands and get a tattoo.

499
00:22:58,380 --> 00:22:59,850
I even held my ID card

500
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:01,880
and took those kinds of photos.

501
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:02,920
What nude loan?

502
00:23:03,030 --> 00:23:04,160
He said he felt sorry for me.

503
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:05,190
So I figured

504
00:23:08,310 --> 00:23:09,510
she was probably just
following their instructions...

505
00:23:09,510 --> 00:23:10,480
To witness our love...

506
00:23:10,480 --> 00:23:11,480
Then he went and got the same tattoo

507
00:23:11,480 --> 00:23:12,520
as me.

508
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:21,920
[Police]

509
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:42,550
I'm sorry.

510
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:45,420
I had so many things to do today.

511
00:23:45,750 --> 00:23:46,440
I'm late.

512
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:47,900
Sorry to keep you waiting.

513
00:23:48,750 --> 00:23:49,960
You are really busy.

514
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:51,070
I

515
00:23:52,270 --> 00:23:53,270
can tell.

516
00:23:58,640 --> 00:23:59,510
Are you okay?

517
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:06,080
It's all my fault.

518
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:09,250
I felt like I was drugged.

519
00:24:10,120 --> 00:24:12,150
I believed whatever Yu Kexin said.

520
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,680
This Yu Kexin

521
00:24:13,970 --> 00:24:15,500
seems to know you very well.

522
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:18,160
She hits all your weak spots.

523
00:24:19,070 --> 00:24:20,920
She lost her father in childhood,

524
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:22,920
met the wrong guy like Li Changning,

525
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:24,920
and both were pitifully hurt.

526
00:24:26,740 --> 00:24:29,270
She said the tattoo
was because of a nude loan,

527
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:32,080
and Xia Yi said the same thing
about Leilei.

528
00:24:32,700 --> 00:24:33,960
And I just believed it.

529
00:24:35,150 --> 00:24:36,700
I didn't even question it.

530
00:24:37,350 --> 00:24:38,750
Maybe they are all liars.

531
00:24:39,490 --> 00:24:41,020
Could they know each other?

532
00:24:42,550 --> 00:24:44,580
Xia Yi is Leilei's ex-boyfriend.

533
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:47,050
Leilei must have mentioned you to him.

534
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:49,080
They exchanged information

535
00:24:49,310 --> 00:24:50,830
and plugged all the holes

536
00:24:50,830 --> 00:24:52,370
that would make you suspicious.

537
00:24:52,370 --> 00:24:54,500
At the same time, they used your guilt,

538
00:24:54,840 --> 00:24:56,270
because you are still
in grief and self-blame

539
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:58,420
over losing Leilei.

540
00:24:58,440 --> 00:25:00,020
So it's easier to believe

541
00:25:00,510 --> 00:25:02,840
Yu Kexin, who faked a similar experience.

542
00:25:08,870 --> 00:25:11,070
What I can't forgive myself for the most

543
00:25:11,790 --> 00:25:13,270
is how I could believe

544
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:15,000
that Leilei

545
00:25:15,550 --> 00:25:17,950
would get a tattoo,
and take out a nude loan.

546
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:23,680
Do you feel

547
00:25:25,590 --> 00:25:27,050
that you betrayed Leilei?

548
00:25:34,030 --> 00:25:36,110
How could I doubt Leilei like this?

549
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:39,000
I'm her best friend.

550
00:26:00,550 --> 00:26:01,590
Drink less.

551
00:26:02,150 --> 00:26:04,350
Getting drunk won't solve the problem.

552
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:07,860
Listen,

553
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:10,880
we are human.

554
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:13,960
Making mistakes is our factory setting.

555
00:26:14,660 --> 00:26:15,450
What's more,

556
00:26:16,060 --> 00:26:18,670
this scam was tailor-made for you.

557
00:26:19,060 --> 00:26:20,450
If it were any of us,

558
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:22,940
it'd be hard to guarantee
not being scammed.

559
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:25,240
Don't blame yourself like this.

560
00:26:29,470 --> 00:26:30,930
You act like a superwoman,

561
00:26:31,370 --> 00:26:33,940
trying your best to protect Li Changning,

562
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:34,720
Yuan Ye,

563
00:26:34,990 --> 00:26:36,700
and even Yu Kexin.

564
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:38,160
Do you know why?

565
00:26:44,860 --> 00:26:47,720
You blame yourself
for your best friend's suicide,

566
00:26:47,990 --> 00:26:49,720
and that's why.

567
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:55,240
You are trying hard to make up for

568
00:26:55,830 --> 00:26:57,880
the regret of not helping Leilei.

569
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,680
Those who always save others

570
00:27:07,850 --> 00:27:08,650
are actually

571
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:10,960
saving themselves.

